data: MANDATORY information session for all candidates running for Student Council. Will take place at 3:40 in the library.

Artist Alley is RHHS' very own annual art show brought to you by Art Council! Students from all over RHHS are invited to showcase and sell any of their artwork. It's an event full of great vibes, yummy snacks, and of course, some fantastic art! Find us on May 30th after school in the caf!
Pre-recorded speeches for the Student Council elections are shown to homerooms.
Candidate posters will be placed around the school for campaign week.
Vote for next year's student council members! Students will be able to vote all day via Google Forms.
